---
description: Single Responsibility Principle (SRP)
globs:
  - "**/*.py"  # Apply to all Python files
  - "**/*.pyi" # Apply to Python stub files
alwaysApply: true
---

Ensure that each class and function has a single, well-defined responsibility or purpose. Avoid creating 'god objects' or overly long functions that handle too many distinct tasks. If a class/function seems to be doing too much, suggest refactoring it into smaller, more focused units.

